{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset employs a BILOU labeling scheme for entity tagging and sentiment classification.",
    "Fine-tuned BERT and Fin-BERT models significantly outperform Chat-GPT in this task.",
    "Additionally, the FinEntity dataset has been applied to cryptocurrency news (15,290 articles from May 2022 to February 2023), demonstrating stronger correlations between entity-level sentiment and cryptocurrency prices compared to traditional sequence-level sentiment models.",
    "Only the test set from the FinEntity dataset is used, with no additional preprocessing applied.",
    "However, we do not consider the start and end boundary tags during evaluation; they are therefore excluded from the assessment."
  ]
}